flowchart TB
    subgraph "Scheduler Platform Overview"
        User([User]) --> Create[Create Schedule]
        Create --> Config[Configure Job<br/>SQL, HTTP, or PowerShell]
        Config --> Timing[Set Timing<br/>Cron Expression]
        Timing --> Enable[Enable Schedule]
        Enable --> Quartz[Quartz Scheduler<br/>Monitors timing]
        Quartz --> Execute[Execute Job<br/>At scheduled time]
        Execute --> Record[Record Results<br/>Success or Failure]
        Record --> Notify[Send Notifications<br/>Email on completion]
    end
    
    style User fill:#4CAF50,color:white
    style Create fill:#e3f2fd
    style Config fill:#fff3e0
    style Timing fill:#f3e5f5
    style Enable fill:#e8f5e9
    style Quartz fill:#2196F3,color:white
    style Execute fill:#fce4ec
    style Record fill:#e1f5fe
    style Notify fill:#f3e5f5
